{"type": "article", "id": 40705, "title": "这套三维建模套装，看起来比乐高更酷｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-11T22:20:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 34, "name": "自行车"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 40327, "name": "百叶窗"}, {"id": 40328, "name": "户外健身器材"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 9425, "name": "Kartell"}, {"id": 40329, "name": "Tokyobike"}, {"id": 40330, "name": "Arckit"}, {"id": 40331, "name": "SolarGaps"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 168, "image": "img/article/article_show/201705112052551So4A2fM0mNIG6tC.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「<b>BestDesign</b>」或是「<b>Qthings</b>」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Arckit Cityscape and Arckit Masterplan by Arckit</h3><p>爱尔兰建筑模型套件制造商 Arckit 有一系列时下流行的模块化建筑设计系统，风格与乐高很相似，用户可以通过该系统自由组合多种模块来创造数字建筑模型。这套城市景观和总体规划三维建模套件，目标受众不只是建筑师和城市规划师类的专业人士，也希望能够吸引到孩童或是爱好者。</p><p>整个套件由模块化的 ABS 塑料零件组成，可拆卸，也可重复使用。城市景观套件提供四种不同的建筑风格，三种尺寸；总体规划套件相较于城市景观套件增加了墙面组建，允许用户构建摩天大楼或是桥梁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=o050225r6mo&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195136afhpCNe9oYDEw2uI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705111951383yVI75Can8TtNwsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195136PCtIgMY9T5qH1jD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.399323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195140xWTXaEi6RZs7kne5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195141pzcTGaPKsVw6gCBJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195143z2RjbESYmsU9wtaN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/10/arckit-next-generation-architects-urban-planners-city-building-kits-architectural-modelling/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Minimalist Outdoor Gym Kebne by Johan Kauppi &amp; Nina Kauppi</h3><p>这套极简主义户外健身器材 Kebne 的设计灵感源自瑞典最高山峰凯布讷山（Kebnekaise），设计师 Johan Kauppi 和 Nina Kauppi 设想的使用场景，是为整个社区提供户外健身器材，Kebne 由五个独立的器材构成，不同的高度和尺寸可以满足不同人群、不同类型的身体锻炼。简单的几何结构，也可以与城市公共空间和景观相融合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0502zhltpa&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195429txh5YvnP1Wbl84Ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195429SBukaGdIVnvgCK1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017051119542949mi6SMkpGg7nPKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195449HBeJl6Vvmaj485ZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195449itQDmOF9JWlVUGIK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195449TDdrqbH3fg9P4aEC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195450fRebzxcLOY6tT82v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://design-milk.com/minimalist-outdoor-gym-inspired-by-a-mountain-in-sweden/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Designer Bicycle Series by Joe Doucet &amp; Calico Wallpaper &amp; Everything Elevated</h3><p>自行车品牌 Tokyobike 最近发布了其第一个设计师系列，参与设计的包括纽约工业设计师 Joe Doucet、来自纽约的壁纸工作室 Calico Wallpaper，以及丹麦设计组合 Everything Elevated 。</p><p>Calico Wallpaper 的作品让人联想到 1930 年代的法国自行车，渐变的褪色效果意在反映从黎明到黄昏的天光变化。Joe Doucet 给出的是一个极简主义的解决方案，白灰两种配色将自行车一分为二，手柄和车座是意大利手工制作出品，他想让使用者变身为一个优雅的骑士；镀铬色彩图案是 Everything Elevated 的亮点，线条流畅的手柄处设计也很抢眼，手把位置明显下移的处理，使得整辆单车像是一辆比赛用车。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195527hu9xKy7PpvORBSYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017051119552637freU4A5ZiuJvbQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Joe Doucet 作品</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195527vnl8cJz5COr9atDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195637HlviMwExbmFIAL5r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Calico Wallpaper 的作品</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195709nYJ1i3tdpymHeOx6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195710G1ST4xMo0mZheR5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Everything Elevated 作品</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Solargaps Smart Solar Blinds by SolarGaps</h3><p>SolarGaps 是一家来自乌克兰的创业公司，他们将目光瞄准了太阳能，将其和百叶窗联系在一起，开发出一套即插即用的太阳能智能百叶窗，可以 24 小时追踪太阳在天空中的角度，生产出清洁的电力。这款智能百叶窗的太阳能电池可以连续使用 25 年，其转化成的电能可以直接使用，也可以存储在家用电池系统中做应急使用。如果将百叶窗安装在窗户外面，每天产生的电力至少可以为 30 个 LED 灯或是三台 Mac 电脑提供充足电力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195746DMZzQnywLHucv4r3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195748TnX7Ea2GULVzKJZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705111957480M28opyEIPKh7d3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195749thugZI4T2JNO15rn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511195749iEjstdBUYupHqeVh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705111957536amP42zxAWtdZMQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/technology/solargaps-smart-solar-blinds-05-10-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Majestic Loves range by Jean Jullien</h3><p>法国知名插画师 Jean Jullien 为葡萄酒品牌 Majestic Wine 设计了一系列打破常规的瓶身包装，仅有图形而无文案。这样做的初衷是想打破传统酒标说明酒的种类、产地、年份等一味追溯复古潮流的做法，而是展现酒本身的感受。Jean Jullien 通过一系列戏剧性的插画，还原了生活中人们可能需要葡萄酒的场合，也将酒本身拟人化，试图说出自己的感受。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705111958334h0f1Jv8CPsQGkWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designweek.co.uk/issues/3-9-april-2017/jean-jullien-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designweek</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200043kCsz1vE57j9Oht2F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705112000432XnRBWK9YUhQvoLr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200043OB5ksb9TqDEplmd1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200044RkAMtOhpqH7EZNgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200044B3kJxmYA2sGth951.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200045RxXmzMvACSOcIsbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200045bLCTmQvXn3iwDh4s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mini Versions of Kartell's Componibili Storage Unit by Nendo</h3><p>Componibili 存储单元是意大利高端家具制造商 Kartell 的畅销产品，是在 1969 年由意大利设计师 Anna Castelli Ferrieri 设计的。为了庆祝产品推出即将满 50 周年，Kartell 最近邀请日本设计事务所 Nendo 重新设计了迷你版本的 Componibili 存储单元。这一系列的特点是外观简洁和功能性强，适用于各种室内装饰环境。因为外观的相似性，即便将这些日常杂物摆在一起，也不觉凌乱，像是葡萄酒瓶、眼镜和花盆配有的滑动小窗和圆形孔，又是其中有趣的点缀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200120OYuSePJcj2i3IDzb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.424281\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200120xhTmCpq2k51jPzKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705112001207fdoigXmn16UO4xh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200120vTLoVBbME0YKw1g2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170511200121qoEU6IMiT7fKZztL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775804\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Dezeen</figcaption></figure></div>"}